data.description: Discover your picturesque 9.55-acre estate with a 2-bedroom house brimming with potential. Home features recent electrical and plumbing updates, along with newer windows and a heat pump for cozy winters. Towering trees offer shade and beauty. With a fresh coat of paint and new carpet, you'll  make it your personal oasis. A newly drilled 20 GPM well ensures ample water for domestic and gardening needs. Only 1.5 miles from Deer Park, enjoy rural tranquility with city convenience. Your country living adventure begins here! Seller is motivated to make a deal with you.
